/********************************************************************************************************************************
 * Register Name: GPIOx_IDR – GPIO port input data register
 * Description  : Reads the logical input level of each I/O pin.
 * Offset       : 0x10
 * Reset Value  : Undefined
 * Configuration:
 * 0: Input is logic low
 * 1: Input is logic high
 * Note:
 * - This register is read-only.
